---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
import ProjectsContent from "../components/ProjectsContent.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold">Coding page</h2>
  <p class="underline decoration-1 decoration-black hover:decoration-2 text-black mt-2 mb-10 "><a href="/">(&lt; back to home)</a></p>
  <p class="text-xl italic">Some of the projects I worked on. They span university coursework, internship work, hackathons and personal projects.</p>
  <p class="text-xl italic">I'm particularly drawn to backend and distributed systems, software architecture, and working across the stack with .NET/C# and TypeScript.</p>
  <p class="text-xl italic mb-10">Always wanting to learn new things and improve my skills.</p>
  <ProjectsContent />
  <p class="text-xl mt-15 italic">More on my <a href="https://github.com/vndrija" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="underline decoration-1 decoration-black hover:decoration-2 text-black">github</a></p>
</Layout>
